{
  "texts": [
    "Accuracy and F1 are then computed using the resulting binary labels.",
    "This relaxed evaluation reduces penalty for fine-grained misclassification between harmful subclasses and measures overall detection capability.",
    "Emotional and Motivational Labeling.",
    "For emotion and motivation annotations, the model predictions are compared with human-reviewed labels using the Jaccard similarity coefficient:",
    "where L LLM and L human denote the sets of emotion or motivation tags assigned to each email."
  ]
}